1) Download and install VirtualBox https://www.virtualbox.org/

2) Download an image for Ubuntu OS 
www.ubuntu.com/download/desktop 

3) Set up a new virtualbox instance named "master"
Linux 
Ubuntu 64 bit 
2 GB RAM 
VDI disk 
Dynamically allocated 

superuser name = master 

4) Point to the Ubuntu OS image you downloaded and install Ubuntu on the VM 


5) Install Java 

$ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/java
$ sudo apt-get update 
$ sudo apt-get install oracle-java8-installer 

6) Install OpenSSH server 
$ sudo apt-get install openssh-server 








